generic_name: ESTRONE, SODIUM CHLORIDE, SEPIA OFFICINALIS JUICE
drug_interactions: Safe - no side effects - no drug interactions - works naturally with your body
dosage_administration: Adults and children 12 years of age and older: Dissolve 2 tablets in the mouth morning and evening until symptoms are relieved. Children under 12 years of age: Not recommended
indications: Temporary relieves premenstrual symptoms such as: bloating, water retention, minor aches, lower back pain, discomfort, emotional changes, irritability
